  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK804">
<l>viḻaitakaiyāṉ vēṇṭi yiruppar keḻutakaiyāṟ</l>
<l>kēḷātu naṭṭār ceyiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If friends, through the right of friendship, do (anything) without being asked, the wise will be pleased with them on account of its desirability.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
